graph LR
  subgraph Vehicle
    Sensors[Sensors<br/>LiDAR/cam/radar]
    Ring[On-vehicle ring buffer<br/>last ~5 min raw]
    Bus[Structured event bus<br/>~100 ev/sec]
    Agent[Telemetry agent<br/>queue + uploader]
    Trig[Trigger detector<br/>hard-brake / anomaly]
  end

  Gateway[Regional ingest gateway<br/>mTLS, schema validation]
  Kafka[(Kafka<br/>structured events)]
  S3[(Object storage<br/>clips)]
  Idx[(Search index<br/>event + clip metadata)]
  Warehouse[(Columnar warehouse<br/>offline analytics)]
  Alerts[Real-time consumers<br/>fleet-ops alerting]

  Sensors --> Ring
  Sensors --> Bus
  Bus --> Trig
  Trig -- snapshot 30s clip<br/>+ context --> Agent
  Bus -- structured stream --> Agent
  Agent -- HTTPS / mTLS<br/>queued, lossy on vehicle --> Gateway
  Gateway --> Kafka
  Gateway -- signed URL upload --> S3
  Kafka --> Alerts
  Kafka --> Warehouse
  Kafka --> Idx
  S3 -. object key .-> Idx
